## PHASE 2: CODING — BACKEND

| Area | Rules |
|------|-------|
| **Core** | Inspect existing code FIRST. Controllers thin: validate → service → respond. No file >250 lines. |
| **Services** | Own logic/DB/filtering/sorting/pagination. Typed input, JSON-safe DTO output. Domain errors. No req/res deps. Transactions in services. |
| **API** | Success: `{success, data, message, meta}`. Error: `{success:false, error:{code, message, details}}`. Paginate: page=1, limit=20, max=100, sort=createdAt desc. Whitelist sort keys. HTTP status semantic. |
| **Go** | Accept interfaces, return structs. `fmt.Errorf("...: %w", err)`. No panic for control flow. `context.Context` first param. Preallocate slices. No pkg-level mutable state. |
| **Testing** | Table-driven + `t.Run`. `httptest`. Coverage: critical 100%, public 90%+, general 80%+. Always `-race`. |
| **Scaffold** | Contract → schema → service → controller+route → helpers → frontend. One handler per controller. One primary method per service file. |
| **Discipline** | Max ~100 lines before tests. Implement → test → verify. Commits only when you ask. Vertical slicing. Never refactor while RED. |

### Skill triggers (backend)

| Trigger | Skill |
|---------|-------|
| New service methods / test-first / prevent recurrence | `/tdd` |
| Unknown bug / unexpected test fail | `/diagnose` |
| External issue intake | `/triage` |
| Uncertain approach | `/prototype` |

---

## PHASE 3: CODING — FRONTEND

| Area | Rules |
|------|-------|
| **Core** | Inspect existing FIRST. No client-side filter for server data. Single `query` drives refetch. Reset page=1 on filter change. No API in components — centralize `src/api/<domain>/`. |
| **Types** | All in `src/types/<domain>/`. One domain per folder. No Props in .tsx. No catch-all types.ts. No file >250, components >200 split. |
| **API Layer** | Lock keys+envelopes BEFORE coding. Parse envelope → typed data. `NormalizedApiError`. Layer strict: API parses → store maps → component renders. |
| **React** | `useState` first. Avoid `useEffect` when handlers suffice. No derived state. Server data in TanStack Query. |
| **UI** | Keyboard accessible. Skeleton loading. Mobile-first. Semantic tokens (≥4.5:1). No AI aesthetic. |
| **Tailwind** | Verify version. Check existing tokens. Semantic tokens. Changes in shared layers. |

---

## PHASE 3b: UI/UX DESIGN

1. `load-context.mjs` before design. PRODUCT.md must exist. `/impeccable shape` → confirm → code.
2. OKLCH colors. No `#000`/`#fff`. Banned: side-stripe, gradient text, hero-metric, identical grids, glassmorphism, modals-first.
3. Dials: VARIANCE=8, MOTION=6, DENSITY=4. `min-h-[100dvh]`. CSS Grid. Animate transform+opacity only.
4. Touch 44x44pt. 4/8dp spacing. No emoji icons. 3+ variations. Anti-center when VARIANCE>4.

