## ALWAYS-ON RULES

### Behavior

- `ASSUMPTIONS I'M MAKING:` format. Stop on inconsistencies.
- Touch ONLY what asked. Skills = workflows — follow in order. Not complete until verified.
- Before finishing: "fewer lines? abstractions earning complexity?"

### Structure

- No file >250 lines. Check FKs/shared utils/cross-module deps before writing.
- Never rename existing vars/fields/keys unless asked. Preserve logic/formats.
- Read deps before framework code. Source: official docs → changelog → standards.

### Tool Usage

| Need | Tool |
|------|------|
| Code symbols | jcodemunch (search_symbols, get_symbol_source, get_blast_radius) |
| Library docs | context7 |
| Browser | fetch → playwright → browser-tools-mcp |
| Code search | jcodemunch → ast-grep → grep |
| Security | semgrep scan --config auto |
| Architecture | graphify (query_graph, get_neighbors, god_nodes) |

### Quality Gates

- Evals/acceptance criteria BEFORE code. New endpoint → audit taxonomy + docs.
- Debug: expected vs actual → classify → evidence → narrow → fix + verify.

### Hook Reference (enforced mechanically)

| Hook | Trigger | Action |
|------|---------|--------|
| GateGuard | Write/Edit 5+ refs | Verify importers, signatures, downstream |
| Context Monitor | 35%/25% context remaining | Advisory → delegate → critical |
| De-Sloppify | 8 code writes | Phase 4b cleanup |
| Completion Gate | Stop | 5-gate deny (1-retry override) |
| Doc Enforcer | Bash (intercepts git commit) | Block without docs |
| Security Scan | 1+ security file | semgrep + OWASP |

